{"type": "article", "id": 28408, "title": "竹子音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161344qPvDCoe5yd8SxEGs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在做音响这件事上，<a href=\"http://www.hazang.net/\">Hazang</a> 的设计团队有一个不太一样的点子：创始人 Bruno Chandon 曾在越南游历了一年并与当地的竹艺工匠 Chung 成为了朋友，他们决定将传统工艺与先进组件融合在一起，创造一款市面上没有的竹子音响。每一个 Hazang 音响都采用越南当地的材料，由工匠精心制作而成。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1299448184/hazang-luxury-bamboo-speakers-handcrafted-in-vietn\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 195 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161340AxBeg4RZastELHVq.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52794118\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613414d6NckpzgHhYZtuq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35787923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021613420J8jPLMHduFkUW53.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49852941\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161342z2RhCEWdiuwmLygZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}